SECTION 6: Z_min BOUND (M21 THM 6.2, NON-CM HECKE LIFT)
------------------------------------------------------------------------

M21 Theorem 6.2 (non-CM Hecke rank lift, M21 SHA verified above):
  For a non-CM modular curve X_0(N) with genus g >= 2,
  the Hecke rank Z satisfies:  Z >= 2*g + 1.

Consequence: genus >= 5  =>  Z >= 11  =>  Z > 10  =>  H2-fail.

      N   genus   Z_min  Z>10?
     67       5      11  YES
     73       5      11  YES
    103       8      17  YES
    107       9      19  YES
    167      14      29  YES
    191      16      33  YES
    193      15      31  YES
    223      18      37  YES
    227      19      39  YES
    229      18      37  YES
    269      22      45  YES

All PREDICT_FAIL primes have Z_min > 10:  PASS

